# Vendored CivMC plugin primitives. Reviewers MUST verify these hashes when
# accepting any PR that touches libs/. CI runs `shasum -a 256 -c` against this
# file on every build.
#
# To refresh: download the new release from the source URL, replace the jar,
# recompute with `shasum -a 256 libs/<file>.jar`, and update the matching line.

